headline: Discover How Federal Realty Continues to Thrive as a Dividend King With Innovative Property Upgrades
summary: Add in a well-above-market dividend yield of 4.9%, and income investors should be very interested in this high-yield REIT.  What does Federal Realty do?  From a big-picture perspective, Federal Realty's business is centered around owning retail properties.
